  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Hogares Luteranos el Buen Pastor ~ Light &amp; Life for Persons with IDD, II</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Hogares Luteranos el Buen Pastor (HLBP) desires to enhance the quality of life of people with intellectual and developmental disabilities (IDD) in the Dominican Republic where there are limited to no public services for this marginalized population. 
The project aims to directly support, expand and sustain services for 29 individuals, including persons with IDD and their support staff, through the following outcomes: 
1) A safe, familial, well-staffed group home for orphaned children with IDD 
2) People with IDD trained and working in the Thrift Store, a vocational pilot program, located at the group home 
3) A consistent, renewable energy source (solar panels) providing power to the group home 
.</narrative>
  </description>
